{"tid":711962,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家身邊有冇一啲女仔係咁？","createTime":"2018-06-21T21:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T08:12:06.000Z","uid":155450,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"818bf91cba6bfcf9f5944ea9f2f7ba1215803f8c","tid":711962,"uid":155450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T21:02:39.000Z","msg":"身邊有啲女仔，佢地個樣唔差但又稱唔上係好靚，性格都有啲缺點，但係無論男定女都係會好保護或好錫佢地，一大班人行啲男仔會圍住佢身邊轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢就算同男仔好close都唔會比人感覺係佢地有野/姣，女仔之間唔多唔少都會有妒忌心 但自己同佢相處果陣都不知不覺會想遷就佢/唔捨得嬲佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家有冇遇過呢啲女仔？其實好羨慕佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點做到咁撚有保護慾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e8912c035f8289bf1b9ed5ba750b7151003bc9","tid":711962,"uid":155450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T21:21:00.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae86c1cb2144a5abd4a530edb7bb7c5a65a309d2","tid":711962,"uid":51196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T21:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca0a974bc0c81892ca7ab73705acf98652ba3d4","tid":711962,"uid":145617,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T22:30:16.000Z","msg":"有啊，生得矮，幾可愛"},{"pid":"26fec7f2fbf1c974adcf9456b4cfbcb5e57c738d","tid":711962,"uid":126977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T22:35:46.000Z","msg":"唔好羨慕我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8087a7d6a316868b0322d4607752ebbc5a1251d0","tid":711962,"uid":76883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T22:37:32.000Z","msg":"冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746069ad0d4ffb3b8bc47cab0c9619d5762a1d9a","tid":711962,"uid":14269